Create the Adoption Analytics App
Guided setup walks you through creating an app from the Adoption Analytics template.
Required editions and user permissions:
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.

User permissions needed to create and manage the Adoption Analytics app:
Access Adoption Analytics Templates and Apps
Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps

User permissions needed to use the Adoption Analytics app:
Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps

In the Analytics tab or Analytics Studio, select Create then App and select the Adoption Analytics template to open the guided flow.
Choose whether to create an app or use the settings from an existing app, and click Continue.
Enter the number of days of data that you want CRM Analytics to store.
To prevent a user’s data from being retained, add the user’s 18-character Salesforce ID to the GDPR_Legal_Compute node in the dataflow.
Click Looks good, next.
Give your app a name, and click Create.
title: Creating the Adoption Analytics App in Salesforce
